      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That makes sense. So if we're looking at that transition, would you say that modern civilization is basically just the natural end goal of human social evolution? Like, is it more \"advanced\" in a way because of those complex systems, or are they just different?",
